224 inline bool CFastColor::operator==(const CFastColor& vector) const
225 {
226  int elementsCount = GetElementsCount();
227 
228  if (elementsCount != vector.GetElementsCount()){
229  return false;
230  }
231 
232  for (int i = 0; i < elementsCount; ++i){
233  if (qAbs(operator[](i) - vector[i]) > I_BIG_EPSILON){
234  return false;
235  }
236  }
237 
238  return true;
239 }

248 inline bool CFastColor::operator<(const CFastColor& vector) const
249 {
250  int commonSize = qMin(GetElementsCount(), vector.GetElementsCount());
251 
252  for (int i = 0; i < commonSize; ++i){
253  if (operator[](i) > vector[i] + I_BIG_EPSILON){
254  return false;
255  }
256  else if (operator[](i) < vector[i] - I_BIG_EPSILON){
257  return true;
258  }
259  }
260 
261  return GetElementsCount() < vector.GetElementsCount();
262 }
